# Space Calibrator agent rules

Quest SLAM + lighthouse continuous calibration fork (`1.5.1-gore-contcal7`).

## Before coding

Read when touching the area:

- [README.md](README.md) — problem statement and fork features
- [docs/ROADMAP.md](docs/ROADMAP.md) — phase status and ceiling
- [docs/P4_TUNING.md](docs/P4_TUNING.md) — cont-cal parameter tuning
- [docs/DEPLOYMENT.md](docs/DEPLOYMENT.md) — SteamVR driver deploy

## Project map

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Continuous calibration | `src/overlay/Calibration*.cpp`, `GuardianDrift.*` |
| UI / presets | `src/overlay/UserInterface.cpp`, `Configuration.*` |
| IPC / driver | `src/overlay/IPCClient.*`, `src/driver/` |
| Profiles | `profiles/` (example presets; personal P4 winners are gitignored) |
| Deploy | `scripts/deploy.ps1`, `scripts/validate-install.ps1` |

## Build notes

- CMake/MSVC Windows project; build output under `bin/`
- Bump `src/common/Version.h` when IPC or driver protocol changes
- Do not commit personal `profiles/p4-*.json` or log artifacts